reviews.review_text: Wow Bob wow they finished playing in the band in buffalo Jerry said " how you all doing" and what a setlist The Hendrix riff during drums the Eyes of the World great he's gone great setlist great show the Grateful Dead. If you like good books puppies and BirdSongs your going to love this!!!

Awesome tape and upgrade It was so hard to get a good tape upfront and get it all at the right levels. This remix is absolutely stellar. It puts the listener right in the front again.
The show is smokin',  two days later is the July 4th the Dead released on DVD. I remember these shows distinctly. Playin took three days to finish! 
"They played the sh*t out of that !" was our quote for the summer in '89...
Thanks Taper Danny and Droncit
